\gamma^\lambda(t)=\gamma(t)+(\lambda)n_s(t)
\implies
\frac{d\gamma^\lambda(t)}{d s^\lambda}\frac{ds^\lambda}{dt} = \frac{d\gamma(t)}{ds}\frac{ds}{dt}+\lambda\frac{dn_s(t)}{ds}\frac{ds}{dt}
